1
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:08,061
<i>At the end of the Ice Age,
the Machine came. </i>

2
00:00:09,033 --> 00:00:12,363
<i>It came from outside.
It came from space. </i>

3
00:00:13,367 --> 00:00:15,094
<i>It came with one purpose... </i>

4
00:00:15,733 --> 00:00:18,325
<i>to change Man into Mutant. </i>

5
00:01:22,864 --> 00:01:24,762
<i>After much suffering and death... </i>

6
00:01:25,098 --> 00:01:27,291
<i>a warrior named Neachdainn... </i>

7
00:01:27,631 --> 00:01:29,824
<i>united the ancient tribes of Man. </i>

8
00:01:31,398 --> 00:01:36,126
<i>Together, they sealed the deadly
Machine beneath the earth. </i>

9
00:01:55,697 --> 00:01:57,686
<i>In the distant mountains
of eastern Europe... </i>

10
00:01:57,897 --> 00:02:00,954
<i>only The Brotherhood,
descendants of Neachdainn... </i>

11
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:03,855
<i>kept knowledge of
the Machine alive... </i>

12
00:02:04,264 --> 00:02:09,196
<i>in stories, in myths, in the
sacred book of The Chronicles. </i>

13
00:02:15,063 --> 00:02:19,791
<i>Years later, four Corporations
ruled the world. </i>

14
00:02:20,496 --> 00:02:21,962
<i>Mishima in the East... </i>

15
00:02:22,663 --> 00:02:25,322
<i>Bauhaus and Imperial
in Europe and Africa... </i>

16
00:02:26,263 --> 00:02:28,229
<i>Capitol in the West. </i>

17
00:02:29,763 --> 00:02:32,092
<i>Each Corporation fights each other... </i>

18
00:02:32,563 --> 00:02:36,995
<i>for what little resources
remain in a war without end. </i>

19
00:02:39,463 --> 00:02:41,326
<i>On the muddy planes of Europe... </i>

20
00:02:41,695 --> 00:02:43,694
<i>the Bauhaus Corporation prepares... </i>

21
00:02:43,729 --> 00:02:46,093
<i>for another assault
on the Capitol lines. </i>

22
00:02:46,862 --> 00:02:52,488
<i>Between them, beneath them,
the Machine still waits. </i>

23
00:02:56,629 --> 00:02:58,561
Keep it up, lads, put a smile on it.

24
00:02:59,228 --> 00:03:02,922
Will you put that
fucking cigarette out!

25
00:03:05,562 --> 00:03:09,551
Alright, you Bauhaus bastards,
what's on today's menu of shit?

26
00:03:16,462 --> 00:03:18,325
Incoming!

27
00:03:18,628 --> 00:03:20,288
Get your lid on, son.

28
00:03:20,494 --> 00:03:21,926
Tuck in! Tuck in!

29
00:03:28,228 --> 00:03:29,318
Keep your heads down.

30
00:03:31,694 --> 00:03:32,682
Enjoy!

31
00:03:39,361 --> 00:03:41,691
Don't pick at it, son.
It makes it worse.

32
00:03:45,728 --> 00:03:47,125
Fucking hell.

33
00:03:51,994 --> 00:03:53,789
All the fun of the fair, eh?

34
00:03:58,860 --> 00:04:00,758
