94
00:12:12,881 --> 00:12:14,176
Motherfuckers.

95
00:12:30,213 --> 00:12:32,838
Jesus, God Almighty, Christ!

96
00:12:47,346 --> 00:12:48,676
Murderer!

97
00:13:06,479 --> 00:13:07,603
Put down your weapons!

98
00:13:08,446 --> 00:13:10,207
Whoa, whoa, whoa, easy.

99
00:13:10,379 --> 00:13:11,605
Has war driven you mad?

100
00:13:11,778 --> 00:13:13,005
My men didn't do this.

101
