210
00:24:46,493 --> 00:24:50,187
I shall return to my
brothers and sisters.

211
00:24:52,626 --> 00:24:57,820
How will you get there? The city
is under siege on all sides.

212
00:25:00,893 --> 00:25:02,324
It shall be as God wills.

213
00:25:03,526 --> 00:25:04,957
"As God wills"...

214
00:25:07,059 --> 00:25:09,252
yes, perhaps it will be.

215
00:25:11,659 --> 00:25:15,022
I have a ship. It won't hold twenty.

216
00:25:15,758 --> 00:25:17,418
You'll have to make do with less.

217
00:25:19,125 --> 00:25:21,421
Take these.

218
00:25:22,758 --> 00:25:25,690
- And what are they?
- Off world tickets.

219
00:25:26,725 --> 00:25:29,691
They should help you recruit
some men for your mission.

220
00:25:32,592 --> 00:25:34,285
Why are you doing this?

221
00:25:36,158 --> 00:25:41,056
