worthy of my attention.

224
00:25:53,325 --> 00:25:55,291
Sir! The perimeter's fallen!

225
00:25:55,624 --> 00:25:58,113
They're hard upon us!
Your ship's ready.

226
00:25:58,258 --> 00:26:01,883
