we have very little time.

229
00:26:10,958 --> 00:26:12,321
God bless you, Constantine.

230
00:26:13,457 --> 00:26:15,753
I sincerely hope so, Brother.

231
00:26:17,924 --> 00:26:19,355
Brother Samuel?

232
00:26:20,957 --> 00:26:23,821
