gosh, has it been that long?

245
00:28:37,186 --> 00:28:38,482
Here's your tea.

246
00:28:40,987 --> 00:28:42,509
Nobody told you?

247
00:28:43,587 --> 00:28:45,280
No, they won't tell me anything.

248
00:28:48,753 --> 00:28:50,184
On behalf of the Exec...

249
